DOCUMENTATION & CONTEXT STRATEGY:
- Document ALL project context in /docs/ folder: rules, methodology, logic, intended behavior, bugs, issues, improvements
- Use Context7 for all frameworks/libraries instead of training data knowledge
- Ensure every change is intentional with documentation to support/revert it
- Design for seamless chat handoffs with ready-to-use context prompts
- Avoid duplicate work by establishing context proactively

DOCUMENTATION HIERARCHY (in project /docs/ folder):
- AI_MEMORY_REFERENCE.md - Master orientation document for AI assistants
- quickstart/ - New user and AI assistant onboarding guides  
- development/ - Technical implementation details and changelogs
- analysis/ - Standards, compliance, and architectural decisions
- templates/ - Reusable templates and boilerplates

PROJECT INDEX REQUIREMENTS:
- Maintain detailed indices for medium/large projects
- Keep PROJECT_CONTEXT.md updated with current state
- Create SESSION_GOALS.md for current work focus
- Organize documentation hierarchically with clear reference paths
